title: GO SMS Pro Cobalt Glass Theme
creator: dustinb

extendedInfo.description: This is a cool Blue GO SMS Pro Theme 1.This is not a standalone app, you need to download latest amazing GO SMS Pro version in order to apply this theme. You can check GO SMS Pro out by searching "GO SMS Pro" in google market2.To apply the theme within GO SMS Pro: Menu->Theme->Cobalt Glass->Apply.IF THE THEME DOES NOT SEEM TO WORK CORRECTLY, Please E-Mail me before leaving negative feedback. I can resolve the issue and get it working for you 95% of the time if you E-Mail me @ CobaltThemes@gmail.comHuge Thanks to lynkx83 and mamta designz for their help in fixing the issue with applying the theme to devices running Android 4.1+ (Jelly Bean)
